      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NO MORE BEER (7) clocked a decent 18.85 finishing second in a Grade 4/5 at this track last start. Smart effort latest and looks a key chance again here. CANYA FLAVOUR (1) generally flies the lids but last time was always well back and ran below best, finishing seventh (30.83) in a Grade 5 at Q Parklands. Placed the start prior (30.83) at Q Parklands after firing out of the boxes. Has a strong winning record here at this journey. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from five starts. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. MAXIMUM ACE (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing seventh (20.68) last time in a P5 at Capalaba. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Should be thereabouts. DAYTONA BEACH (8) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.",
